OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FFormer Liverpool manager Jurgen Klopp
OL,7,Fcriticised the club's fans for booing
OL,8,FTrent Alexander-Arnold after admitting
OL,9,Fhe had never been so disappointed in
OL,10,Ftheir actions.
OL,12,FThe German, who is beloved on
OL,13,FMerseyside after winning the Champions
OL,14,FLeague, Premier League, FA and League
OL,15,FCups in a nine-year spell which ended
OL,16,Flast summer, said he switched off the
OL,17,Ftelevision when he heard the jeers.
