OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FUnlike his successor Arne Slot, who
OL,7,Fsaid it was not his place to tell
OL,8,Fsupporters how to react, Klopp did not
OL,9,Fhold back in his contempt for their
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,F"I don't want to tell anyone what they
OL,13,Fshould think, I don't want to say what
OL,14,Fyou have to think but I can tell you
OL,15,Fwhat you think is wrong. I am an old
OL,16,Fman and I don't waste time with hiding
OL,17,Fmy opinion," said Klopp, who was guest
OL,18,Fof honour at the LFC Foundation ` of
OL,19,Fwhich he is an ambassador ` Gala Ball.
