OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,F"I watched the game when he came on
OL,7,Fand I heard the booing. I'm old so it
OL,8,Fmy be my hearing so I turned up the
OL,9,Fvolume and said 'That's booing'.
OL,11,F"I needed another 10 seconds to
OL,12,Frealise and then I switched the telly
OL,13,Foff. I honestly could not have been
OL,14,Fmore disappointed in this moment. This
OL,15,Fis not us, 100 per cent.
OL,17,F"I don't tell you you should not be
OL,18,Fdisappointed or angry, I tell you
OL,19,F'Don't forget'. This club does not
OL,20,Fforget. We are famous for not
OL,21,Fforgetting.
