OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,F"We don't forget anything: we don't
OL,7,Fforget the good thing and we don't
OL,8,Fforget the bad thing. But we ignore
OL,9,Fthe bad things and remember the good
OL,10,Fthings.
OL,12,F"You don't have to be happy he is
OL,13,Fgoing but don't forget what he did for
OL,14,Fthis club because I can't forget it."
OL,16,FKlopp listed a whole number of
OL,17,Foccasions in which Alexander-Arnold
OL,18,Fhad delivered for the club and
OL,19,Fstressed without his contribution they
OL,20,Fwould not have had the success they
OL,21,Fdid.
