OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,FThe England international has decided
OL,7,Fto bring an end his 20-year
OL,8,Fassociation with the club when his
OL,9,Fcurrent deal expires in the summer and
OL,10,Fis expected to sign for Real Madrid.
OL,12,FKlopp said that he was well within his
OL,13,Frights to do that and if anyone had
OL,14,Fthe right to be angry it was owners
OL,15,FFenway Sports Group as it was their
OL,16,Fmulti-million asset who was leaving on
OL,17,Fa free transfer.
