OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,F"I was there every day ` if he
OL,7,Fwouldn't have given everything, I
OL,8,Fwould tell you now but every day he
OL,9,Fgave absolutely everything for this
OL,10,Fclub and now, after 20 years, he has
OL,11,Fdecided he wants to go somewhere
OL,12,Felse," added the German, who said he
OL,13,Fhad contemplated attending Sunday's
OL,14,Ffinal match of the season in an
OL,15,FAlexander-Arnold shirt but did not
OL,16,Fwant to detract from the Premier
OL,17,FLeague trophy presentation.
