OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,F"If someone should be angry it should
OL,7,Fbe the owners ` but they are not. 'Why
OL,8,Fdidn't he sign a new contract?'. I
OL,9,Fhear this from fans, this money
OL,10,Fdiscussion: 'He goes without a
OL,11,Ftransfer fee'.
OL,13,F"They (the owners) have to be angry.
OL,14,FNot us but it is not about that. He
OL,15,Fgave absolutely everything and wears
OL,16,Fthe Liverpool badge in the skin.
OL,18,F"This boy, 18 years old, scored a free-
OL,19,Fkick in Hoffenheim where if he doesn't
OL,20,Fscore that we don't qualify for the
OL,21,FChampions League.
