OL,3,CJurgen Klopp criticises Liverpool fans
OL,4,Cfor booing Trent Alexander-Arnold
OL,6,F"Against Barcelona he did the most
OL,7,Fcheeky thing in the world and set up
OL,8,Fthe goal for 4-0, a result and a game
OL,9,Fwhich will not happen again.
OL,11,F"But now he plays next year for
OL,12,Fanother club and we decide how we deal
OL,13,Fwith that."
